Some very interesting information, Eugene!<br /><br />But I seriously doubt that those chips are made by the "real" Hitachi and Toshiba.  They are generically-named clones coming from the usual places, China or Taiwan.<br /><br />The first Dendy system picture that you linked to is the same design as the Micro Genius IQ-501.  Is this the original design of the Dendy?<br /><br />Finally, does the word "Dendy" have any sort of meaning?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=355">ccovell</a> — Sun Apr 19, 2009 3:53 am</p><hr />
